dct_title_s: Ore veins in Warren County map 1867
dct_description_sm: Geological survey map of the iron ore veins in and around property owned by Oxford Furnace. Surveyed and drawn by G. M. Hopkins under the direction of George H. Cook, State Geologist and John C. Smock, State Assistant Geologist.
